               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; two initial lines of the incipit of Text II; two initial lines of sections of Texts I-2 and I-3; the words sälam “salutation”, sǝbḥat “glory” and a few others in Text II; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
A few groups of lines (alternating with black lines) on the incipit page of Text I.</rubric>
